sequenceDiagram
    participant TB as ThingsBoard
    participant API as flood-api
    participant G as flood-gateway
    participant M as mosquitto
    participant A as actuator
    participant DB as influxdb

    Note over TB,API: 3 nguồn lệnh, 1 mặt phẳng điều khiển MQTT
    G-->>M: 1) lệnh tự động từ rule engine
    TB->>G: 2) RPC v1/gateway/rpc (setPump…)
    G-->>M: dịch RPC → lệnh
    API-->>M: 3) REST POST /command
    M->>A: basin/{st}/actuator/command
    A->>A: áp dụng pump / gate / siren / board
    A->>M: basin/{st}/actuator/status
    M->>G: status
    G->>DB: ghi actuator_status
    G-->>TB: mirror status lên cloud
